*FvwmButtons kill    	bomb_3d.xpm   	Destroy
*FvwmButtons(1x1, Swallow(UseOld)	FvwmPager 'FvwmPager * *')
*FvwmButtons(1x1, Swallow "xload" "Exec nice -16 \
		xload -nolabel -update 4 -bg grey59 -geometry -1500-1500")

